Description: A beautiful and secure CLI tool for managing SSH connections
SSH Keeper is a modern TUI application for managing SSH connections
with secure password storage and beautiful interface.
.
Features:

- Browse and search SSH connections
- Add new SSH connections easily
- Secure password storage
- Export/Import OpenSSH config compatibility
- Modern TUI with colors and animations
- Fast and lightweight Go implementation
